Sensitive skin isn’t just a phase—it needs extra TLC. 💆‍♀️
If your skin stings, burns, or reacts easily, it’s telling you something. Don’t guess with skincare—always patch-test and consult a dermatologist before trying new products.

Because with sensitive skin, less is more—and expert guidance is everything💜

Products in the video:
Physiogel Hypoallergenic Daily Moisture Therapy Dermo-Cleanser For Dry & Sensitive Skin
Clinikally Hyaluronic SkinBooster Serum
COSRX Lightweight Soothing Moisturizer
